TEXT.S: = Sbunaw = Gaga mniq Tawyuensu Fusingcyu ka alang Sbunaw. 48 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 179 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 97% niqan 174 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 3% niqan 5 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 87%, Amis 1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, ni rahuq na o 9%.
